# 🎰 Unity Slot Machine Game

## 📌 Overview

This project is a slot machine game developed in Unity using C#. It focuses on delivering smooth gameplay, structured code, and interactive UI while simulating real-world slot machine mechanics.

The design emphasizes clarity, modularity, and user experience, aligning with core game development principles.

---

# 🧾 Evaluation-Based Highlights

## ⭐ Core Functionality Implementation

* Fully functional 3-reel slot system
* Randomized spin outcomes
* Snap-to-symbol stopping logic for accuracy
* Result evaluation after all reels stop
* Separate logic for normal spin and betting system

---

## ⭐ Code Cleanliness & Structure

* Clear separation of concerns:

  * `GameControl.cs` → game logic & state
  * `Row.cs` → reel mechanics
* Event-driven architecture using delegates
* Minimal redundancy and readable naming conventions
* Organized state handling using flags (e.g., spin state, bet mode)

---

## ⭐ Reel Animation & Game Feel

* Smooth reel spinning using coroutines
* Gradual slowdown effect for realism
* Seamless looping of reel positions
* Snap alignment ensures clean visual stopping
* Audio feedback synchronized with reel motion

---

## ⭐ Git Commit History & Repo Quality

* Structured project with clear file separation
* Logical grouping of scripts and assets
* Ready for version control with meaningful modular design
* Easily extendable architecture

---

## ⭐ Bonus Features / Creative Additions

* Betting system with risk-reward logic (+200 / -200)
* First bet guaranteed win (user engagement design)
* Dynamic result popup system
* Real-time balance tracking
* Spin sound integration for immersion

---

## ⭐ UI/UX Clarity

* Simple and intuitive interface (Roll / Bet)
* Context-based UI visibility (buttons appear after spin)
* Popup feedback for every result
* Clear text indicators:

  * Jackpot
  * Win
  * Loss
* Clean layout with focus on usability

---

# 🎮 Gameplay Features

* 🎰 3 spinning reels
* 🔁 Randomized results
* 💰 Betting system
* 🔊 Spin audio feedback
* 📊 Live balance updates
* 🪟 Result popup display

---

# 🧠 Technical Approach

* Coroutine-based animation system
* Event-driven reel triggering
* Position-based symbol detection
* Controlled game state transitions
* Lightweight and efficient update handling

---

# 📂 Project Structure

* `GameControl.cs`
  Handles:

  * Game state
  * UI updates
  * Betting logic
  * Audio control

* `Row.cs`
  Handles:

  * Reel spinning
  * Symbol alignment
  * Stop detection

---

# 🚀 Possible Improvements

* Adjustable betting amounts
* Reel-by-reel stopping delay
* Advanced animations (bounce, glow effects)
* Sound effects per reel stop
* Win streak or multiplier system

---

# ✅ Conclusion

This project demonstrates a strong understanding of Unity fundamentals, including animation handling, UI interaction, and structured game logic. It balances simplicity with functional depth while maintaining clean and maintainable code.
